*rspec-core-2.14.8-r4 (04 Jan 2015)

  04 Jan 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +rspec-core-2.14.8-r4.ebuild,
  -rspec-core-2.99.2.ebuild, rspec-core-3.1.7.ebuild:
  Add rspec 2.14.8 revision that does not install /usr/bin/rspec, and let rspec
  3.x block on it to avoid file collisions, fixing bug 534420.

*rspec-core-3.1.7 (28 Dec 2014)

